<HEADLINE>
<P>
A TELEVISION 'RING' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I watched that mess, even "Gotterdammerung," which lasted almost five hours. 
</P>
<P>
I was waiting for the Rhine to rise and wash away Valhalla -- and those stupid 
gods with it. That never happened. 
</P>
<P>
And the ring itself -- it was supposed to give the owner power to rule the 
world. But when push comes to shove, it can't even hold off Brunnhilde's 
attacker. Some ring! 
</P>
<P>
DALE RICHARDSON 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
