<P>
KPFK (RADIO STATION); 1965 (RADIO PROGRAM); WATSON, JOHN G; HOMOSEXUALS; RADIO 
AUDIENCES; YOUTH; CENSORSHIP 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA063090-0069 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 240931 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
