EVIDENCE; WITNESSES; PRISONERS RIGHTS; PRISONERS -- CALIFORNIA; ATTORNEYS; 
LEGAL ETHICS; JUDGES -- CALIFORNIA; CRIMINAL LAW 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
