<SUBJECT>
<P>
BRUSH FIRES -- ORANGE COUNTY; ARSON -- ORANGE COUNTY; DIAGNOSTIC TESTS; 
PSYCHOLOGICAL TESTS; BRUSH FIRES -- SANTA BARBARA COUNTY; ARSON -- SANTA 
BARBARA COUNTY; POLICE INVESTIGATIONS; FORENSIC SCIENCE; MURDERS -- SANTA 
BARBARA COUNTY; REWARDS; BRUSH FIRES -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; ARSON -- LOS 
ANGELES COUNTY; BRUSH FIRES -- SAN BERNARDINO COUNTY; ARSON -- SAN BERNARDINO 
COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
