MAGAZINE HONORS EX-CORONA DEL MAR VOLLEYBALL STANDOUT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jason Perkins of USC, a former standout at Corona del Mar High School, has been 
named to Volleyball Monthly magazine's all-freshman team. 
</P>
